Sitting here not doing much of anything.Just digesting after a big cookout. The amount of things that run through my head is endless. Its an array of thoughts that always linger. I guess i'll just set myself up for failure then the reward is so much sweeter and if there is no reward its no big deal i didn't think i would get it anyway. I know i'm just blabbing about nothingness and you have no idea what i am speaking of. But i guess i'm just venting. I want something and i don't know what to do about it. I'm stoked....yet not.
I'll just keep on livin'
keep on lovin'
keep on truckin'
and KEEP on believin' cause he knows whats best.
<333 ME
